            <div class="title">
                India (Transfer Of Power)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-06-03/debates/167f9b02-2bbc-46be-a568-e5567415b027/BusinessOfTheHouse" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
